    "body" : "Are you using the XA libs?  <a href=\"http://ora-02089.ora-code.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">ora-02089.ora-code.com</a>  Similar thread: <a href=\"https://community.jboss.org/message/515056?_sscc=t\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">community.jboss.org/message/515056?_sscc=t</a>"
