  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/11936220/oracle-ora-02089-with-java",
  "title" : "Oracle ORA-02089 with Java",
  "body" : "<p>I'm getting the following error when trying to call a PL/SQL stored procedure from Java: <code>ORA-02089: COMMIT is not allowed in a subordinate session</code></p>\n\n<p>It tests fine from Oracle. Does anyone have any experience with this? </p>\n"
